{"tid":2235952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警員追捕時失平衡跪地受傷 16歲男生被控襲警押後裁決","createTime":"2020-10-09T05:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T06:13:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"00a9c74b0eead87c0122f28419f53144136bffa1","tid":2235952,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月發起「七區行街」行動，當晚警方在柴灣阻止示威者堵路。有警員追捕16歲男生時，疑兩度遭男生推開致失平衡跌倒，跪地拗傷。男生事後被制服，遭控襲警罪，今日受審。追捕被告的警員在辯方盤問下承認，部份遇襲細節是今天出庭作供時才首次提及，惟否認被告從沒推他之說。<br />\n<br />\n16歲被告否認一項襲警罪，案件今在東區裁判法院開審。柴灣警署特遣隊警員11030曾偉強供稱，去年11月3日晚上9時許，得悉柴灣道迴旋處有示威者堵路，於是與同袍到場拆路障及掃蕩嘗試堵路者。及後他在怡豐街近怡泰街交界聽到有人大叫：「唔好走！」「唔好跑！」並看見被告向他迎面跑來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/VTTTE2X7C5CYZDBUB5RGEPQ5LQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FVTTTE2X7C5CYZDBUB5RGEPQ5LQ%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=54b342ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FVTTTE2X7C5CYZDBUB5RGEPQ5LQ%2F&h=87ee5f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/VTTTE2X7C5CYZDBUB5RGEPQ5LQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b1f9856b7ec0bd46e617c3a749cd3ec221e06149","tid":2235952,"uid":304769,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"死黑警真係好野，自己仆街都可以告人，真係威L過習近平"},{"pid":"fb49a3ca794aeaf7fbd36312fc804f64cec4d79a","tid":2235952,"uid":69746,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔告埋地下？"},{"pid":"d61caff2276151e6f026c7a87528bc8c8c100af0","tid":2235952,"uid":57205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"追捕被告的警員在辯方盤問下承認，部份遇襲細節是今天出庭作供時才首次提及<br />\n<br />\n一年時間度好哂講稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f8fd9a71c1918c74a6f80aa404b38ea752873b","tid":2235952,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202